This game is a clone of Warlords II by the Strategic Studies Group (SSG), 
but the most important feature of this game is freedom.  For more information 
about using software in its fullest sense, go to www.fsf.org.

This game is licensed under the terms of the GNU General Public License version 3 or (at your option) any later version.

For more information on how to play LordsAWar!, see: 
http://www.nongnu.org/lordsawar/manual/
